GLOBAL
- Spell components: common (candles, chalk, salt, iron filings) at apothecaries;
  rare (void-crystal shards, ashfall mineral residue, pyramid copper) require
  specialist brokers or expeditions
- Enchanted items: Violet Compact registry catalogued dangerous artifacts —
  later exploited by Spirebound Conclave to process condemned persons through
  the same legal channel as dangerous items
- Withered Depths blight (near Kiess): orphaned Conclave crystals in forest
  root systems still propagate; approach with caution
- Void-corruption: Void Citadel artifacts carry corruption after separation;
  handle through intermediaries; do not carry in open containers
- Psionic vs arcane: psionicists draw from internal reserve; some counter-
  spellcasting enchantments do not affect psionic effects
- Alchemy: unlabeled potions should be tested; mixing unknown potions is
  how people die
- Black Sun Shard anti-light leaks into the Gloamvault (below Midgaard);
  detection magic reads differently in those spaces
~
